  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A study to determine the effect on renal function in renal transplant patients with biopsy
      proven Chronic allograft nephropathy (CAN) nephropathy who are switched from a Calcinerin
      inhibitor (CI) triple drug regimen to a Rapamycin based triple drug regimen or maintained on
      their CI protocol
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
